name: Celer cBridge
highlight: Fast, secure and low-fee asset bridge that supports 130+ tokens across 30+ blockchains
summary: Celer cBridge is a decentralized and non-custodial asset bridge that supports more than 130 different tokens across 30+ different blockchains and layer-2 rollups. Built with the Celer Inter-chain Messaging Framework, cBridge has processed more than $9b cross-chain transfer volume for more than 192K unique users.
